    DRYRUN:
            1. Android #F5F1835 ko parse karega
            2. # ka matlab hexadecimal number hai
            3. F5 = Red component ka value (245)
            4. F1 = Green component (241)
            5. 83 = Blue component (131)
            6. 5 = Alpha/transparency? (Actually ye 6 digit hona chahiye,
                   yahan 7 digits hain - probably typo)
            7. Is color ko apply karega background par

    COLOR FORMAT:
            #RRGGBB ya #AARRGGBB
            RR = Red (00-FF), GG = Green, BB = Blue, AA = Alpha
            #FF0000 = Red, #00FF00 = Green, #0000FF = Blue
    -->

